Argument order:

1.Number of matrices used per evaluation (required)
2.Number of generations to run for (required)
3.Number of runs to do (required)
4.Simulated Annealing constant (required, but if SA mode off it wont do anything)
5.Number of mutations (required)
6.Toggle simulated annealing (optional) (off by default, SA to toggle on)
7.Toggle cap mode (optional) (on by default, nocap to toggle off)
8.Toggle greedy mode (optional) (off by default, pos to toggle on)
